## Platform [/platforms/id?include=includes]
Get a single Platform object 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Platform to perform action with. Has example value.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `devices`, `platformVersions`, or `all`

